Package: rewind
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Architecture: ARCH_PLACEHOLDER
Maintainer: andu <andu.ucsd@gmail.com>
Depends: libc6
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/anduaura/rewind
Description: Deterministic replay of distributed system incidents
 rewind attaches an eBPF agent to running containers and captures all
 inter-service HTTP/gRPC traffic, outbound DB calls, and non-deterministic
 syscalls. A triggered flush produces a .rwd snapshot that can be replayed
 locally to reproduce any production incident exactly.
 .
 Record: rewind record --services api,worker --output incident.rwd
 Flush:  rewind flush --window 5m --output incident.rwd
 Replay: rewind replay incident.rwd --compose docker-compose.yml
